# World Cup API
The **World Cup API** lets you manage World Cup games.

# Group Games
Game related resources.





## Game Collection [/games]

+ Model

    + Body
    
            [
                {
                    "id": 1, 
                    "home": "Brazil",
                    "guest": "Croatia",
                    "location": "Sao Paolo",
                    "result": "3:1"
                }, 
                {
                    "id": 2, 
