                    "location": "Natal"
                }
            ]
        
### List all Games [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    [Game Collection][]

### Create a Game [POST]
+ Request (application/json)

            {
                "home": "Brazil",
                "guest": "Spain",
                "location": "Belo Horizonte"
            }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

            {
                "id": 49,
                "home": "Brazil",
                "guest": "Spain",
                "location": "Belo Horizonte"
            }

## Game [/games/{id}]
A single game.

+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the game.

### Retrieve a Game [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Header

            X-My-Header: The Value

    + Body

                {
                    "id": 1, 
                    "home": "Brazil",
                    "guest": "Croatia",
                    "location": "Sao Paolo",
                    "result": "3:1"
                }

+ Response 404

### Remove a Game [DELETE]
+ Response 204
